            <li class="aside-item br-6 f-row f-justify-between fs-2 pointer">
                <a href="/how-to-play">How to play</a>
            </li>
            <li class="aside-item br-6 f-row f-justify-between fs-2 pointer">
                <a href="/blog/">Blog</a>
